vote.title: An ordinance abandoning portions of a water easement, four sanitary sewer and water easements and a water-wastewater easement to 6070 NCX LLC, the abutting owner, containing a total of approximately 14,807 square feet of land located near the intersection of North Central Expressway and Twin Sixties Drive - Revenue: General Fund $6,400.00, plus the $20.00 ordinance publication fee
